東留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打打算渣車定租車?<br />\n<br />\n我睇過台灣好行d車好疏，一日得10班8班車<br />\n可能好浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未甩p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該步兵或者單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同女朋友慢慢hea遊<br />\nbtw之前台南行路好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我p都未有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都諗住同女友踩下單車咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大馬路好繁忙，但條路夠闊唔會危險<br />\n記得台灣紅燈都可以轉彎"},{"pid":"efde143e87318d03cb91c337717beb024144d23f","tid":50133,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:50:20.000Z","msg":"係女。我幫到你。<br />\n我3月會去花蓮自駕"},{"pid":"0db094e0f4929a39cee116f82678f5fcd09b1380","tid":50133,"uid":35927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T10:25:14.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"6bc3afaf3b9a6c4ae2e110a442d0d439762cf933","tid":50133,"uid":70497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T01:19:59.000Z","msg":"如果渣車啲路同燈難唔難"},{"pid":"8ac7226b7018d7b6179d691311d84199aa34f80e","tid":50133,"uid":20979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T04:16:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講瑞穗牧場好普通 仲要坐個幾鐘火車<br />\n睇海可以包車去石梯坪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n花蓮市冇咩好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n景點好散同埋好遠<br />\n<br />\nBtw幕谷幕魚因爲之前打風依家封左，去之前記得查下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為朋友話想去瑞穗牧場, 咁我又順手可以去附近睇下茶園同買下茶。本身打算HEA遊, 點知PLAN PLAN下都唔HEA。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一陣就上機, 好緊張呀"},{"pid":"e8172fecd7b044d5a11c9f45e12a4177fd6846f1","tid":50133,"uid":59211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0