blockquote><br />\n頭尾8日呀</blockquote><br />\n行程plan好左？ 定係隨心？"},{"pid":"58716a4ee405985f7c04f75635f4f45514c52659","tid":50133,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:15:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟1星期後出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去花蓮+台東</blockquote><br />\n幾幾多日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頭尾8日呀</blockquote><br />\n行程plan好左？ 定係隨心？</blockquote><br />\n頭2日2夜係花蓮<br />\n主要去太魯閣7星潭<br />\n之黎台東山線海線市中心各1日<br />\n之黎再住1晚知本溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d7d28df9652a120124abc9cfb5d1d374cd0f3c","tid":50133,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>推一推先<br />\n岩岩plan左少少<br />\nday1 夜晚去到，夜市算<br />\nday2 日月潭+太魯閣<br />\nday3-4 豐濱鄉<br />\nday5 慕谷慕魚<br />\nday6 hea下就回港<br />\n<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打自駕？<br />\nday2好chur下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我跟local tour去太魯閣+清水斷崖都玩左全日到5點<br />\n有無可能去埋日月潭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我見順路以為玩到咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽完你講，跟你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日月潭好遠喎<br />\nGoogle Map 揸車都要四個半鐘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4405a553d324f39a79a3dd963a47751cf943ed","tid":50133,"uid":57523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:05:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>推一推先<br />\n岩岩plan左少少<br />\nday1 夜晚去到，夜市算<br />\nday2 日月潭+太魯閣<br />\nday3-4 豐濱鄉<br />\nday5 慕谷慕魚<br />\nday6 hea下就回港<br />\n<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打自駕？<br />\nday2好chur下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我跟local tour去太魯閣+清水斷崖都玩左全日到5點<br />\n有無可能去埋日月潭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我見順路以為玩到咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽完你講，跟你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日月潭好遠喎<br />\nGoogle Map 揸車都要四個半鐘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你屌打我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我其實想講七星潭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成件事會唔會合理d?"},{"pid":"bfb992685de8494e852464b6bf91a5fedf6601be","tid":50133,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T15:59:08.000Z","msg":"買左機票6月去8日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88078ec377e229a69586f9e289d15bd55cf21870","tid":50133,"uid":59041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T01:39:18.000Z","msg":"前年去過，自己揸機車，無牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n七星潭景靚，對住太平洋，hea下幾好，<br />\n上面話day tour,七星潭+太魯閣，其實幾趕，太魯閣上面好多條步道，㨂好先去，<br />\n不過老實，個陣我中午食完，一野轟過去，有啲步道深入小小都唔夠時間去，你當觀下景行下山咁，<br />\n市內冇乜野行，夜市人多得黎普通，<br />\n上面講既慕谷慕魚幾有特色，但入去前要先申請，有去個段時間封左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5475be17591c299be2178780bd8b2e80c4293e3","tid":50133,"uid":48163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T04:42:39.000Z","msg":"小弟下個月去，夾得時間嘅再因為晏機去早機返實際得兩個 full day 玩。<br />\n<br />\n第一次去花蓮，聽完睇完各位巴打分享，太魯閣應該係必去。<br />\n<br />\n反而第二日就仲度緊， 老人家假如平日喺香港行吓山，去慕谷慕魚辛唔辛苦？<br />\n<br />\n都唔肯定係咪封山，有人話係，但有人話啱啱去完&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"2b5f161831e8763919c7b0b05cf17443d44a5a6a","tid":50133,"uid":79788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T04:58:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟下個月去，夾得時間嘅再因為晏機去早機返實際得兩個 full day 玩。<br />\n<br />\n第一次去花蓮，聽完睇完各位巴打分享，太魯閣應該係必去。<br />\n<br />\n反而第二日就仲度緊， 老人家假如平日喺香港行吓山，去慕谷慕魚辛唔辛苦？<br />\n<br />\n都唔肯定係咪封山，有人話係，但有人話啱啱去完&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n一樣呀喂都係下個月去 <br />\n去就三日但下午uo到第三日要上午走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為之前已經去過台東所以唔打算行花東縱谷<br />\n今次plan左行一個步道 七星潭 同新城天主堂個邊行下"},{"pid":"019fb0eb9e5512a612afcc7b0b750347c0781fc0","tid":50133,"uid":73232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:27:30.000Z","msg":"花蓮公車班次少，建議搭的同佢傾好去邊同咩價錢。<br />\n有d花蓮嘅小市鎮就搭火車都得架啦"},{"pid":"8fb99e3406a7f44a5222a915eb7e902823ddf510","tid":50133,"uid":13849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:56:53.000Z","msg":"黎緊四月尾都一個人去花蓮六日 留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dcfb969ad1389863e02af5ed7b58afaaef4c440","tid":50133,"uid":90025,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:58:38.000Z","msg":"上年12月去完嚟，分享下太魯閣交通<br />\n如果巴絲係去行步道，我行咗最簡單嘅三個：砂卡礑、綠水、燕子口<br />\n無錯係有個巴士一／兩日券<br />\n但係巴士係好疏嘅同埋啲站分佈唔係好friendly<br />\n<br />\n咁都算，如果行以上步道，綠水同燕子口切記要原路折返<br />\n<br />\n砂卡礑封咗一半，但應該都係要返返出原路<br />\n<br />\n燕子口都好啲，唔算長，出口可以行返隧道返去，不過唔建議<br />\nGoogle到呢張圖，可以參考下個行程<br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.hiking.biji.co/static/upload/55ad1d24086fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.hiking.biji.co%2Fstatic%2Fupload%2F55ad1d24086fd.jpg&h=210f0b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綠水，條路就唔難行，但係去到岳王廟係搭唔到任何巴士<br />\n而去到慈母橋真係要夾啱時間，而且觀光巴係唔停，隨時唔啱時間要等好耐<br />\n除咗觀光巴，張票只包兩三條好疏嘅local線<br />\n另外就只有一條張票唔包，一架一個鐘一班（算密）嘅路線（太魯閣客運302）<br />\n又係Google出嚟同一個site嘅圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.hiking.biji.co/static/upload/54c60f851574d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.hiking.biji.co%2Fstatic%2Fupload%2F54c60f851574d.jpg&h=870aac07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過以上三條個景都幾靚（綠水就得一個位觀景，上面張圖「斷崖」之處），我覺得比起日本個大步危更加壯絕<br />\n<br />\n至於天祥，其實無咩睇，有間麻麻地嘅餐廳（好似三間咁其實係同一間），一間7-11，祥德寺，同埋文天祥公園<br />\n<br />\n或者巴絲們其實可以跟佢建議嘅行程比較穩陣<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.taiwantrip.com.tw/line/19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.taiwantrip.com.tw%2Fline%2F19&d=nzSJVo1IAPnrs9zyhenr%2BWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=a77a4558\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.taiwantrip.com.tw/line/19</a><br />\n<br />\n最後，可以去公園官網睇下有無封路<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.taroko.gov.tw/zh-tw/Event/TrailCondition?id=111\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.taroko.gov.tw%2Fzh-tw%2FEvent%2FTrailCondition%3Fid%3D111&d=nzSJVo1IAPnrs9zyhenr%2BWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=96ee1068\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.taroko.gov.tw/zh-tw/Event/TrailCondition?id=111</a>"},{"pid":"98f70c6c2d0622f8cbd8afe24c49f23d50a99422","tid":50133,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T12:29:27.000Z","msg":"早上8點機係咪只可以的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eccf0becdd753dc4bdc7767915a94ed28271b77","tid":50133,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T12:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早上8點機返香港係咪只可以的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ea3cae0b82db409ff9734d629693f4b5854c27ca","tid":50133,"uid":90025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T13:46:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟下個月去，夾得時間嘅再因為晏機去早機返實際得兩個 full day 玩。<br />\n<br />\n第一次去花蓮，聽完睇完各位巴打分享，太魯閣應該係必去。<br />\n<br />\n反而第二日就仲度緊， 老人家假如平日喺香港行吓山，去慕谷慕魚辛唔辛苦？<br />\n<br />\n都唔肯定係咪封山，有人話係，但有人話啱啱去完&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote><br />\nGoogle咗, 已解封"},{"pid":"d2b17c2ed158e19eb72be2b8f3171db84414abef","tid":50133,"uid":90025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T13:48:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早上8點機係咪只可以的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早一晚返台北啦<br />\n就算有火車你都要凌晨3-4點走"},{"pid":"d27451e51953d3c275bfa695c567ab0f7f36d071","tid":50133,"uid":61546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T14:13:12.000Z","msg":"如果得一個full day喺花蓮做咩好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想去瑞穗"},{"pid":"6093b2b0026e44ff4343fefec84dcdec77c0ed91","tid":50133,"uid":11077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T17:28:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果得一個full day喺花蓮做咩好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想去瑞穗</blockquote><br />\n啱啱去完瑞穗得d 牛同兩隻鴕鳥<br />\n仲有一間小食店賣牛奶同饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好細 食埋嘢最多一粒鐘閃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021b01a3914a27016ac1eeb5160d4196af0f03af","tid":50133,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T03:06:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早上8點機係咪只可以的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早一晚返台北啦<br />\n就算有火車你都要凌晨3-4點走</blockquote><br />\n但我訂左早上8點機係花蓮返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed99c7f08ee6201722ebe530c691373bcd550de","tid":50133,"uid":29747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T03:10:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前年去過，自己揸機車，無牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n七星潭景靚，對住太平洋，hea下幾好，<br />\n上面話day tour,七星潭+太魯閣，其實幾趕，太魯閣上面好多條步道，㨂好先去，<br />\n不過老實，個陣我中午食完，一野轟過去，有啲步道深入小小都唔夠時間去，你當觀下景行下山咁，<br />\n市內冇乜野行，夜市人多得黎普通，<br />\n上面講既慕谷慕魚幾有特色，但入去前要先申請，有去個段時間封左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊到有得租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}